children.label: getCreateControlButton
description: Returns a button that allows controls to be created externally using the embeddable

children.label: closePopover
description: Closes the create control menu popover when flyout opens - only necessary if `buttonType === 'toolbar'`

returnComment:
If `buttonType == 'toolbar'`, returns `EuiContextMenuPanel` with input control types as items.
Otherwise, if `buttonType == 'callout'` returns `EuiButton` with popover containing input control types.
